                            configuration processes, Stalwart Labs set out to create a modern, all-in-one mail server
                            solution.</p>

                        <p>Stalwart Labs is growing rapidly. While the project initially started with one developer, the
                            company is now expanding its team, actively hiring backend and frontend developers, support
                            staff, and specialized sales personnel to better serve our expanding customer base.</p>

                        <p>With a presence in both the UK and the US, Stalwart Labs is dedicated to delivering
                            innovative, secure, and easy-to-maintain email server solutions. Our mission is to drive the
